data.title: Michael Welch Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Michael Welch with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Identifies as Jewish

Made his feature film debut playing Artim in Star Trek: Insurrection, the ninth installment of the beloved Star Trek film series

Known for playing the popular Mike Newton in the Twilight Saga film series, though he originally auditioned for the part of Edward Cullen

Was the USO's celebrity guest in 2010 for their first USO educational tour, and worked with over 600 students and spent time with wounded soldiers

Is heavily involved with youth oriented non-profit The Thirst Project, which builds fresh water wells in developing communities
